dct_title_s: Mercer, Middlesex, and Monmouth Counties, New Jersey 1913
dct_description_sm: Farm Journal map of Middlesex, Mercer, and Monmouth counties. The map has a printed note reading: "The roads in each township are numbered and correspond with the Farm Journal Farm Directory of the County." Counties are not seperated but townships are seperated by yellow lines.
Some wear on edges of map and along folds.
